Q: Define desire.
<br>A: Desire is an expression of I-am-ness which only works for self-interest.
In self-interest, there is only wanting objects.
<br>Q: Desire for understanding, knowledge of truth?
<br>A: That too is wanting, guided by the ego. That too goes away when supreme dispassion dawns. <span class=date>12/19/96</span>
